# The live non-secret network-core configuration is committed in
# `network-core.auto.tfvars`.
#
# Use this example file only for local overrides or temporary experiments that
# should not become part of the shared infrastructure source of truth.
#
# The parent network-core root keeps legacy RouterOS credentials only while the
# nested DHCP stack migration is in progress.
#
# Typical local-only inputs during the migration window:
# mikrotik_password = "replace-me"
